areas, should be developed from a realistic point of view, and
concentrate on basic agricultural technology.
</P>
<P>
He encouraged young people in government departments to work in
rural areas as teachers, schoolmasters or local township or
village officials.
</P>
<P>
These trained youths then can lead farmers in their efforts to
develop local rural economy, and also learn valuable lessons from
this practical experience.
</P>
<P>
During his trip to Shanxi, Li visited businesses, villages and
colleges and universities.  
