<HEADLINE> Euro-Asian Railway Will Promote Economic Development </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ALMA ATA, July 5 (Xinhua) -- The Euro-Asian Continental Bridge
(EACB), a rail network linking eastern China with western Europe,
will play a major role in the economic development of Central
Asia, Chinese Foreign Minister Qian Qichen said today.
</P>
<P>
