Housing Minister Meir Porush to hand over control to Sharon of two
departments under his ministry.
</P>
<P>
Porush refused Netanyahu's requests to give up the Public Works
Department, which handles road infrastructure and employs more
than 1,000 people, and the Rural Construction Administration that
supervises construction of kibbutzim and small
settlements. 
