<HEADLINE> Privatization Data Centres to Be Set Up in Zambia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LUSAKA, July 6 (Xinhua) -- the Zambian government will set up
privatization control centres at the six divisions of the Zambia
Consolidated Copper Mines (ZCCM) to facilitate the privatization
of the mining conglomerate.
</P>
<P>
