</P>
<P>
Taipei: min. 26 degrees c., max. 35 degrees c., cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Guangzhou: min. 26 degrees c, max. 35 degrees c., clear to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
