<HEADLINE> Pudong, Hot Investment Spot in China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 6 (Xinhua) -- Pudong New Area in Shanghai has
attracted more than 10 billion US dollars of direct overseas
investment from 56 countries and regions, today's " Shanghai
Securities News" reported.
</P>
<P>
During the first half of this year, overseas investors put
1.538 billion US dollars into 430 new projects in Pudong, bringing
the total of overseas-funded projects there to 3,931.
</P>
<P>
Pudong has attracted 60 multinational firms to invest in 99
local projects.
</P>
<P>
In addition, more than 20 billion yuan of domestic investment
has also flowed into the area.
</P>
<P>
During the first half this year, the area registered 159
domestic-funded enterprises, bringing the total to 4,388.
</P>
<P>
Foreign trade companies nationwide have opened 45 subsidiaries
in Pudong.  
</P>
